ğŸ”“ Step 6: Add Port 3000 to EC2 Security Group
Go to AWS EC2 Dashboard

Navigate to: Instances â†’ Security Groups

Click on your instance's security group

Click Edit Inbound Rules

Add a rule:

Type: Custom TCP

Port: 3000

Source: 0.0.0.0/0

Save

